HEADWORD: Embrown
<hw>Em*brown"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>em-</ets> (L. <ets>in</ets>) + <ets>brown</ets>.]</ety> <def>To
